{"tid":1395614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線既人唔該入黎！！！點樣撤退？","createTime":"2019-08-01T21:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T21:53:58.000Z","uid":260740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b60869e40f0326fcb7d41f13461ab17d8af883d7","tid":1395614,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T21:00:34.000Z","msg":"有一點想提<br />\n前線如果突然去圍某地區警署<br />\n之後出嚟嘅人（後排）有好多其實都係當區嘅街坊<br />\n街坊絕對可以散得好快（唔係講笑，保安亦唔會比防暴入去）<br />\n前線一直想後排走先<br />\n所以唔走住<br />\n但後排係怕一走你地就被包圍<br />\n因為後排可以極速化整為零入各屋苑<br />\n絕對可以數分鐘內消失晒（如果近屋苑）<br />\n<br />\n戰術或前線既人請思考一下遇到這種情況時的撤退方法"},{"pid":"938c29506b50d3f5d2d2061911d51bafa20902a9","tid":1395614,"uid":260740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T21:21:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4876fe9a230f4406d72cf1114c3376eb53fda40","tid":1395614,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T21:52:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb16a882f9b730dc8beaf9bf4b662fa953deb6eb","tid":1395614,"uid":64938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T21:53:58.000Z","msg":"[香城online]傳令兵的技巧和心得<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n就快又發夢啦，手足幫手廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}